internalDatabase.query:
-- Enable extension
CREATE EXTENSION IF NOT EXISTS pgcrypto;

-- Create table with all columns, including composite_id, first
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS "{{data.var.tranzettaTable}}" (
    price_id UUID PRIMARY KEY DEFAULT gen_random_uuid(),
    price_key TEXT,
    price_type TEXT,    
    price_code TEXT,
    sku TEXT,
    price NUMERIC(12,4),
    break_qty NUMERIC(12,4),
    promotional TEXT,
    description TEXT,
    customer_id TEXT,
    customer_name TEXT,
    customer_price_class TEXT,
    uom TEXT,
    warehouse TEXT,
    effective_date TEXT,
    expiration_date TEXT,
    created_at TIMESTAMP DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
    updated_at TIMESTAMP DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP
);

ALTER TABLE "{{data.var.tranzettaTable}}"
DROP CONSTRAINT IF EXISTS "{{data.var.uniquePriceKey}}";

ALTER TABLE "{{data.var.tranzettaTable}}"
ADD CONSTRAINT "{{data.var.uniquePriceKey}}" UNIQUE (price_key);

-- Create the last_execution_of_flows table with an auto-populated primary key
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS last_execution_of_flows(
    flow_key TEXT PRIMARY KEY,
    tenant_id TEXT,
    flow TEXT,
    trigger_type TEXT,
    last_execution TIMESTAMP
);
SELECT (last_execution) FROM last_execution_of_flows WHERE tenant_id = '{{data.var.tenantId}}' AND flow='{{data.var.flowName}}'

INSERT INTO "{{data.var.tranzettaTable}}" (
    price_key, 
    sku, 
    description, 
    customer_id, 
    customer_price_class, 
    break_qty, 
    promotional, 
    price,
    uom,
    warehouse,
    effective_date, 
    expiration_date,
    price_type,
    price_code,
    created_at,
    updated_at
) 
VALUES (?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, CURRENT_TIMESTAMP, CURRENT_TIMESTAMP)
ON CONFLICT (price_key)
DO UPDATE SET
    customer_id = EXCLUDED.customer_id,
    sku = EXCLUDED.sku,
    description = EXCLUDED.description,
    customer_price_class = EXCLUDED.customer_price_class,
    break_qty = EXCLUDED.break_qty,
    promotional = EXCLUDED.promotional,
    price = EXCLUDED.price,
    uom = EXCLUDED.uom,
    warehouse = EXCLUDED.warehouse,
    effective_date = EXCLUDED.effective_date,
    expiration_date = EXCLUDED.expiration_date,
    price_type = EXCLUDED.price_type,
    price_code = EXCLUDED.price_code,
    updated_at = CURRENT_TIMESTAMP;
